homepage.hero.text.message: Here, I will share the problems and solutions in various technology stacks, take you to a deeper understanding of the latest technology trends, and show their application in actual development. I hope my development experience can provide you with inspiration and help you solve the challenges in your project more efficiently.

theme.project.description.message: The true meaning of learning lies in being able to apply what you have learned in practice, rather than just staying in theory. Every learning journey lays a solid foundation for application. What is shown here is the result of my continuous efforts in the technical field. I firmly believe that only the ability to transform knowledge into practical operations can truly bring out the value of learning.

theme.movie.description.message: Here is the best proof of my hard practice and application in the field of technology.

features-1.message: As a full-stack engineer, mastering both front-end and back-end skills is essential for independently handling project development and maintenance.

features-2.message: My passion for programming has sharpened my code reading skills. No code is too difficult—only a choice to understand it. Through self-discipline and continuous learning, I keep improving and tackling challenges.

features-3.message: Have extensive experience in helping others solve programming problems, covering a variety of technical fields from front-end to back-end.
